{\tc\tcl2 \v Installation}
{
\par
\pard\plain \s140\fi-360\li360\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
1.\tab create new project in the STM32CubeIDE\par
\pard\plain \s140\fi-360\li360\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
2.\tab copy the content of {\f2 Examples/Test_Step_Motor.c}  into the {\f2 {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAASJ" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 main.c}}}}  of your project\par
\pard\plain \s140\fi-360\li360\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
3.\tab copy the {\f2 system_stm32f4xx.c}  from {\f2 CMSIS/Src/}  to {\f2 YOURPROJECT/Src/} \par
\pard\plain \s140\fi-360\li360\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
4.\tab change the properties of your project{
\par
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
1.\tab open the properties of your project then expand {\f2 C/C++ Build}  \'E2\'86\'92 {\f2 Settings}  \'E2\'86\'92 {\f2 MCU Settings}    { \field\flddirty {\*\fldinst  INCLUDEPICTURE "mcu-settings.png" \\d \\*MERGEFORMAT}{\fldrslt Image}}
   \~\par}
{
\par
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
1.\tab make sure {\f2 Floating-point unit}  is set to {\f2 FPv4-SP-D16}  \par
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
2.\tab set the {\f2 Floating-point ABI}  to {\f2 mix HW/SW implementation (-mfloat-abi=softfp)} \par
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
3.\tab expand {\f2 C/C++ Build}  \'E2\'86\'92 {\f2 Settings}  \'E2\'86\'92 expand {\f2 MCU GCC Assembler}  \'E2\'86\'92 {\f2 Include paths}  and add the following paths: {
\par
\pard\plain \s42\li720\widctlpar\adjustright \shading1000\cbpat8 \f2\fs16\cgrid "$\{workspace_loc:/Balancer\}"\par
"$\{workspace_loc:/MCAL\}"\par
"$\{workspace_loc:/CMSIS\}"\par
}
\par}
{
\par
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
1.\tab expand {\f2 C/C++ Build}  \'E2\'86\'92 {\f2 Settings}  \'E2\'86\'92 expand {\f2 MCU GCC Compiler}  \'E2\'86\'92 {\f2 Include paths}  and add the following paths: {\f2  "$\{workspace_loc:/Balancer\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/MCAL\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/CMSIS\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/MCAL/Inc\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/MCAL/Inc/mcalTimer\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/CMSIS/Include\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Include\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/Balancer/Inc\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/Balancer/Src\}" } \par
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
2.\tab expand {\f2 C/C++ Build}  \'E2\'86\'92 {\f2 Settings}  \'E2\'86\'92 expand {\f2 MCU GCC Linker}  \'E2\'86\'92 {\f2 Libraries}  \'E2\'86\'92 {\f2 Libraries (-l)}  and add the following text: {\f2  {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACL" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 Balancer}}} MCAL CMSIS } \par
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
3.\tab on the same page in the {\f2 Library search path (-L)}  section add these paths: {\f2  "$\{workspace_loc:/Balancer/Inc\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/Balancer/Src\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/Balancer/Debug\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/MCAL/Debug\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/MCAL/Debug/Src\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/MCAL/Debug/Src/mcalTimer\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/CMSIS/Debug\}" "$\{workspace_loc:/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates\}" } {
\par
\pard\plain \s142\fi-360\li1080\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
1.\tab expand {\f2 C/C++ General}  \'E2\'86\'92 {\f2 Paths and Symbols}  select the {\f2 Debug}  configuration. Open the {\f2 References}  tab and make sure the checkboxes of the following items are checked: {\f2  {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACL" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 Balancer}}} MCAL CMSIS } \par}
}
\pard\plain \s140\fi-360\li360\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
