{\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACL" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 Balancer}}} firmware entry point. }}\par
{\s17\sa60\sb30\widctlpar\qj \fs22\cgrid 
Performs peripheral initialisation in the same order as the reference (LED, both I2C buses, ADC, SysTick, SPI to TFT, TFT init+rotation+font, rotary encoder), constructs the central {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACL" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 Balancer}}} aggregate object, sets up the SysTick countdown timers and enters the loop.\par
Loop dispatch:{
\par
