\pard\plain 
{
\pard\plain \s17\sa60\sb30\widctlpar\qj \fs22\cgrid {\s17\sa60\sb30\widctlpar\qj \fs22\cgrid 
Header of the {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACM" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 Balancer_t}}} aggregate. \par
}{\s17\sa60\sb30\widctlpar\qj \fs22\cgrid 
\par
{{\s5\sb90\sa30\keepn\widctlpar\adjustright \b\f1\fs16\cgrid 
Author\par}\pard\plain \s81\li360\widctlpar\ql\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {\s17 \sa60 \sb30
Luis Brunn {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK "https://github.com/LuBru70" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 https://github.com/LuBru70}}}
 \par
}}Defines the central {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACM" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 Balancer_t}}} type, including hardware-object pointers, control objects, operating state, editable parameters, SysTick timers, and method pointers. It also declares the {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAABK" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 TaskModus}}} and {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACK" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 ParamIdx}}} enumerations, the external {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACL" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 Balancer}}} prototype instance, and the {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAAER" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 BalancerCreate()}}} constructor.\par
{{\s5\sb90\sa30\keepn\widctlpar\adjustright \b\f1\fs16\cgrid 
Architecture\par
}\pard\plain \s81\li360\widctlpar\ql\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {
\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9702\tab}\ilvl1\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx720\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
{\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACM" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 Balancer_t}}} is an aggregate following the OOP-in-C pattern: encapsulation, composition, and prototype-copy construction with function-pointer based method.\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9702\tab}\ilvl1\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx720\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
Hardware objects ({\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACN" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 MPU6050_t}}}, {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACP" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 TOFSensor_t}}}, {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACR" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 Stepper_t}}}, {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAAAN" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 analogCh_t}}}) are aggregated by pointer. Their lifetime is owned by {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAASJ" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 main.c}}}.\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9702\tab}\ilvl1\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx720\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
Control objects ({\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACV" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 PIDContr_t}}}, {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACZ" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 MeanVal_t}}}) are composed by value inside {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACM" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 Balancer_t}}}.\par}
}{{\s5\sb90\sa30\keepn\widctlpar\adjustright \b\f1\fs16\cgrid 
