{\s17\sa60\sb30\widctlpar\qj \fs22\cgrid 
@function mpuGetAcceleration\par
This function retrieves acceleration values along the X, Y, and Z axes from the {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAAHZ" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 MPU6050}}} sensor, converts them to physical units in terms of g (gravitational acceleration), and stores them in the {\f2 accel_xyz}  array of the provided sensor instance. If the accelerometer is disabled, the function skips the I2C read and returns an error code.\par
