{\s17\sa60\sb30\widctlpar\qj \fs22\cgrid 
@function BalancerDispAlphaNumMPU\par
Used by the M_DispMpuData diagnostic/debugging mode. Triggers a fresh accel read on the IMU, then prints the three axes one above the other at fixed TFT coordinates.\par
