Reset the {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACM" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 Balancer_t}}} to a clean starting condition. }}\par
{\s17\sa60\sb30\widctlpar\qj \fs22\cgrid 
@function BalancerInit\par
Called once by {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAABDU" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 BalancerCreate()}}} and again whenever a full re-init is required. Performs:{
\par
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
1.\tab Copy defaultParam[] into ParamValue[].\par
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
2.\tab Initialise PID_phi, PID_dist, PID_velo with the parameter values just loaded and the proper TA.\par
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
3.\tab Clear the TOF distance low-pass filter.\par
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
4.\tab Reset every operating-state field (mode, flags, timers, motor positions, route counters).\par}
After return the {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACL" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 Balancer}}} is in M_InitBat, with RunInit set so the first M_Bala / M_DistCtrl entry will perform its initialisation.\par
