{
\pard\plain \s61\li360\sa60\sb30\qj\widctlpar\qj\adjustright \fs20\cgrid 
\par
{
{\s17\sa60\sb30\widctlpar\qj \fs22\cgrid 
Inner balance loop. }}\par
{\s17\sa60\sb30\widctlpar\qj \fs22\cgrid 
@function BalancerUpdatePitch\par
Translation of "case M_Bala" from the reference into a method of the {\field {\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK  \\l "AAAAAAAACM" }{}}{\fldrslt {\cs37\ul\cf2 Balancer_t}}} object. Sequence:\par
{
\par
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
1.\tab RunInit branch (on entering M_Bala):{
\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
Switch TFT to landscape-flip and paint header.\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
Activate stepper hold current and zero positions.\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
Push parameter values into the IMU (pitchZero, swLowPassFilt, pitchFilt, HW DLPF).\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
(Re-)initialise PID_phi.\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
Set the IMU axis remap (RPY[2,3,-1]) which matches the way the MPU is mounted on this robot.\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
Set IMU integration time-base.\par}
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
2.\tab Read pitch from the IMU and run fall detection (|pitch| > PITCH_FALL_RAD -> robot fallen):{
\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
Re-init PID_phi and clear PID_dist/PID_velo to drop integrator wind-up accumulated during the fall.\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
Reduce stepper current (relax the motors).\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
return.\par}
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
3.\tab Determine "actively balancing" state:{
\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
|pitch| < PITCH_ACTIVE -> activeMove = true.\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
Otherwise hold current is kept on but no motor command is issued.\par}
\pard\plain \s141\fi-360\li720\widctlpar\fs20\cgrid 
4.\tab Active PID (pitch) step:{
\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
Clamp pitchOffset to +/- a_pClamp so the outer loop can never destabilise the inner loop.\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
error_phi = pitch - pitchOffset.\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
setPitch = rad2step * PID_phi.run(error_phi).\par
\pard\plain {\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \hich\af3\dbch\af3\loch\f8 \'01\u9642\tab}\ilvl2\ls1 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-360\tx1080\li1080\ri0\lin1080\rin0\fi-360\kerning1\hich\af4\dbch\af5\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs20
Once activeMove is asserted, command ONE motor (left/right alternating via stepRenable toggle)- This keeps the per-call I2C load below the 7 ms timing.\par}
}
